products.title: Mayfair Grey Dimout Perfect Fit
products.productdescription: Update your windows with the exquisite mayfair grey dimout perfect fit, for a charming look to your windows. The smooth grey tone is dappled only by the light and shadow of the blind's ripping pleats, to give an ultra-textured look that would go beautifully with other tactile grey fabrics within your interior.
